description:
Comment: 14 pages and 14 ps-figures, revtex; version to appear in Phys.Rev.D;
  scenarios updated, discussion of numerical results for sqrt{s}=193 GeV and
  sqrt{s}=500 GeV, plots updated

Comment: 27 pages, 7 figures, revtex; several typos corrected; a few
  references added; title changed slightly; includes a "note added in proof";
  version to appear in Phys. Rev. D

Comment: 23 pages, LaTeX2e, 16 PostScript figures, uses graphicx.sty;
  Descriptions on the momentum distribution are enlarged; A derivation of the
  momentum distribution formula is added as an appendix; Other minor changes;
  In ver.4, comparison with O(alfs) final-state interaction corrections to
  momentum distribution added; two figures added

Comment: 19 pages, LaTex, (v2) a comment on black holes with 2 and 3 charges
  added, (v3) some phrases made more precise, references added, minor changes;
  version to appear in Phys. Rev. D

Comment: 17 pages, LaTeX, no figures; v2: Introduction modified, references
  added and typos corrected; v3: Introduction changed; v4: Eq.(12) corrected;
  v5: final version to appear in Phys. Rev. D

Comment: REVTeX, 12 pages, 1 figure in a separate fig1.eps file, 1 table;
  minor corrections in English and misprints; version to be published in Phys.
  Rev. D15
